description:
Hi everyone, 

My roommate and I are renting our nice duplex located in the heart of East Village, 5 min walk from L train and 15 min from Union Square. It's the perfect location to make the most out of NYC night life (tons of bars, restaurants,..) !
name: Beautiful East Village Duplex
review: The host canceled this reservation 8 days before arrival. This is an automated posting.
